---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base
  title="Volunteering — Get Involved"
  description="Volunteer with Friends of Gledhow Valley Woods — join our monthly action mornings, water testing programme, or help at the Green Fair."
  section="get-involved"
>
  <section class="bg-bluebell-800 text-white py-12 relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-bluebell-900 to-bluebell-700 opacity-90"></div>
    <div class="relative max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <nav class="text-bluebell-200 font-sans text-sm mb-4" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
        <a href="/" class="hover:text-white">Home</a> / <a href="/get-involved" class="hover:text-white">Get Involved</a> / <span>Volunteering</span>
      </nav>
      <h1 class="font-heading font-bold text-4xl md:text-5xl text-white">Volunteering</h1>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12 md:py-16">
    <div class="prose prose-lg font-body text-earth-800 max-w-none">
      <p>
        FGVW is run entirely by volunteers, and there are lots of ways to get involved — whatever time you have to give.
      </p>

      <h2 class="font-heading font-bold text-bluebell-900 text-3xl mt-8">Action mornings</h2>
      <p>
        Our regular volunteer work parties carry out practical conservation tasks in the woods — path maintenance, vegetation management, and habitat improvements. No experience or equipment is necessary, and all ages are welcome.
      </p>

      <h2 class="font-heading font-bold text-bluebell-900 text-3xl mt-8">Water testing</h2>
      <p>
        Our <a href="/water-testing">citizen science water quality programme</a> is always looking for volunteers to help monitor Gledhow Beck. Training is provided.
      </p>

      <h2 class="font-heading font-bold text-bluebell-900 text-3xl mt-8">The Green Fair</h2>
      <p>
        Our annual <a href="/green-fair">Green Fair</a> is made possible entirely by volunteers — helping with set-up, stewarding, and running activities on the day.
      </p>

      <h2 class="font-heading font-bold text-bluebell-900 text-3xl mt-8">Committee &amp; trustees</h2>
      <p>
        If you'd like to take a more active role in how FGVW is run, we're always glad to hear from people interested in joining the committee or standing as a trustee.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-10 bg-bluebell-800 text-white rounded-lg p-8">
      <h2 class="font-heading font-bold text-2xl text-bluebell-100 mb-3">Ready to get involved?</h2>
      <p class="font-body text-bluebell-200 mb-5">Get in touch and let us know what you're interested in — we'll point you in the right direction.</p>
      <a href="/contact" class="inline-block bg-white text-bluebell-900 hover:bg-bluebell-100 font-sans font-bold px-6 py-3 rounded transition-colors">
        Contact us
      </a>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-10 pt-8 border-t border-cream-400 flex gap-4 flex-wrap">
      <a href="/get-involved" class="font-sans text-sm font-semibold text-bluebell-700 hover:underline">← Back to Get Involved</a>
      <a href="/get-involved/membership" class="font-sans text-sm font-semibold text-bluebell-700 hover:underline">Becoming a Member →</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
